ArmDemo
=======



Step one, get a compiler:

Compile your own: http://www.arklyffe.com/main/2010/08/29/arm-gcc-toolchain-build/

Or this this binary:
(stolen from http://dev.frozeneskimo.com/notes/cortex_cmsis/ )

gui installer:
https://sourcery.mentor.com/GNUToolchain/package9742/public/arm-none-eabi/arm-2011.09-69-arm-none-eabi.bin

tar ball:
https://sourcery.mentor.com/GNUToolchain/package9740/public/arm-none-eabi/arm-2011.09-69-arm-none-eabi-i686-pc-linux-gnu.tar.bz2



OpenSuse:

install packages:
sudo zypper install libftdi1-devel

patterns:
sudo zypper install -t pattern devel_C_C++


OpenOCD:
http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/openocd/openocd/0.6.1/openocd-0.6.1.tar.bz2
tar -vjxf openocd-0.6.1.tar.bz2
cd openocd-0.6.1/
./configure --enable-ft2232_libftdi
make
sudo make install

Set permissions for usb device:
create new file: /etc/udev/rules.d/40-ngx.rules
with contents:
     ATTRS{idVendor}=="0403",ATTRS{idProduct}=="6010",MODE="0666",GROUP="users"


Bootloader:
upload bootloader.bin

second file starts at 0x2000

